history.content:
Join Girls Who Code @ Berkeley✨ INTRO TO TECHNICAL INTERVIEWS workshop ✨ (beginner-friendly) tomorrow --> Wednesday, April 6th in Institute of Transportation Studies Library (ITSL) - 412 McLaughlin Hall from 6:10 PM - 7:00 PM PST!!

Join us for a careers workshop on the technical interview process! We will go over what to expect in the overall timeline of applying to internships, what to expect in a technical interview, and how you can start preparing now!

WHERE: Institute of Transportation Studies Library (ITSL) - 412 McLaughlin Hall

WHEN: Wednesday, April 6th from 6:10 PM - 7:00 PM

For more information, Check out our Facebook and Instagram @gwcberkeley
